    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Starstruck",
        "Description": "Trevor Jones,  despite his lack of time on the racetrack, revels in the limelight of autographs and lovely ladies.\r\rHis biggest fan, Robyn Haywood, constantly buys Atlantide and any Blue Seed merchandise just to watch him scribble his name in rushed cursive. But other ladies around him notice Robyn getting a bit too close... She doesn&apos;t have the dedication they do, getting jobs at the Grand Innovation Race.\r\rThey want Robyn to be left starstruck, and understand the gravity of the situation.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Ashley.",
